       " \n",
       "\n",
       " \n",
       "Our fiscal 2024 business plan includes an expectation that we invest strategically in new product and service offerings in areas where we can leverage our product development skills, understanding of video technologies and strength in the higher education vertical. These offerings will likely require additional resources in engineering, sales and operations, in order to successfully grow and scale new businesses.\n",
