       "\n",
       " \n",
       "g.\n",
       " \n",
       "\n",
       " \n",
       "COVID has negatively impacted interest and ability to hold in-person events and while virtual events are often held in place of in-person events, some companies and attendees are less likely to hold or attend virtual events.\n",
