       "Overview\n",
       "\n",
       " \n",
       "\n",
       "Sonic Foundry, Inc. is the global leader for video capture, management, and streaming solutions as well as virtual and hybrid events. Trusted by thousands of educational institutions, corporations, health organizations and government entities in over 65 countries with solutions that transform communication, training, and learning. Sonic Foundry’s brands include Mediasite®, Mediasite Connect, Vidable® and Global Learning ExchangeTM.\n",
